{"tid":1658631,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"佩洛西：美國不可以對中國人權狀況視而不見","createTime":"2019-10-16T14:21:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T09:09:02.000Z","uid":141151,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"dc7e1590d0dc1118acc00a9d51cfcdc665872329","tid":1658631,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:21:56.000Z","msg":"佩洛西：美國不可以對中國人權狀況視而不見<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=366406\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D366406&d=Wg3pkMW64ksxbb%2FAt9Sry%2BIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=2e098938\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D366406&h=f32aa302\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=366406</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】美國眾議院通過《香港人權與民主法案》。眾議院議長佩洛西指，美國不可以為了商業利益對中國人權狀況視而不見。<br />\n<br />\n眾議院以口頭表決方式，指《香港人權與民主法案》在至少三分二議員支持下通過，法案要求總統列出名單，制裁打壓香港自由的人，及拒絕他們入境美國。而任何人因為參與支持人權的非暴力抗爭而被捕，國務院亦不應拒向他們發簽證。<br />\n<br />\n國務院須每年向國會交報告檢視香港是否享有足夠自治，符合特殊待遇。<br />\n<br />\n參議院將審議類似法案，兩院之後會合併出一個版本再作表決。<br />\n<br />\n眾議院今次亦同時通過限制催淚彈及橡膠子彈等人群管制裝備輸出到香港的《保護香港法案》，議長佩洛西指美國不可以為了商業利益對中國人權狀況視而不見。"},{"pid":"ec15aac1df0a61e6083101186ace3e6f8c4433dd","tid":1658631,"uid":259787,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T14:22:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oRuZXFG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoRuZXFG.jpg&h=e4ca09bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D4W5TdZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD4W5TdZ.jpg&h=ae2306c2&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QHdv4kF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQHdv4kF.jpg&h=652be563&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gvgd17k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%